About us
Shenzhen WJM is a Silicone&plastic products manufacturer founded in 2002.Our factory is located in Longgang District, Shenzhen, China. With an area of 7000 square meters and employ over 250 workers, Specialized in silicone&plastic products, mainly mobile phone cases, Tablet covers, Silicone & Plastic products manufacturing and developing.
"To Be No.1" is our firmly belief, which has already established good reputation in the industry. Meanwhile we have experienced exporters in management and engineering, and site operators, we can design and produce all kinds of silicone & plastic products according to customer's drawings or samples.
From the designing to molding, finally, delivering, we were able to offer the excellent OEM service for you, currently, more than 80% products are exported to America, Germany, U.K., Spain, Japan, Korea, etc for almost 40 different countries all over the world, Our main clients are Tesco, T-mobile, Wal-mart, Case-Mate, Bushnell, Beyond and so on.
Our factory has passed ISO9001:2008Quality system in 2009, the whole procedure from mass production to inspection was executed strictly according to the ERP system.
Our main products are various kinds of mobile phone cases, tablet protecting covers, Silicone & Plastic products, Conductive keypads, silicone nipple, silicone kitchenware, silicone rings and other components.
With the great hope of cooperating with you, we believe we will be the excellent partners!

ABOUT US
WJM custom case​
Our factory
Our company have precision injection molding workshop, silicone product workshop, precision mold workshop, modern quality packaging production line. We have 12 Silicone molding machines and 12 plastic injection molding machines,there are 8 people in the R&D Department, 20 people in the Silicone Molding Workshop, 15 people in the Injection Molding Workshop, 30 people in the Packaging Workshop, and 15 people in the Quality Control Department. We can control the whole process from R&D to Delivery to provide you with high-quality products.​​​​​​​
Cooperative customers
We have a group of enterprise management personnel, engineering and technical personnel and on-site operators with rich industry experience were brought together. Our main customers are world-renowned companies from Europe and America: TESSCO; BUSHNELL, CASE-MATE, HAMA, etc​​​​​​​
Development history
Set Sail
We help customers to design and produce silicone molds, while the boss made a website, and advertising.In the industry is also an original.
Scaling up
The company expanded to 600 square meters and added new equipment for production.
Started the Foreign Trade
The factory building of 4000 square meters and 10 sets of silicone die-casting machines were added to produce iPod touch for Belkin of the United States and protective cases for Nintendo of Japan (Wii).
Relocation again
Under the circumstances of the global financial crisis, the company bucked the trend and moved to an independent factory with an area of more than 7,000 square meters Then sales began to grow rapidly.
CES Exhibition
In 2009, We participated in CES for the first time and received a large number of orders from ILUV.
PC Molds
We started to design and manufacture plastic molds.
PC Products
The company began to purchase plastic machines for the production of plastic products, and the main products are mobile phone cases of Apple, Samsung and Huawei.
Scaling up again
Since 2011, we have participated in CES in the United States, MWC in Spain, Computex in Taipei, IFA in Germany, Global Resources Electronics Show in Hong Kong, Electronics Show in Brazil, Electronics Show in Japan, etc. In September 2019, in order to meet the growing needs of the company's business, we moved from a 7,000-square-meter factory to an independent industrial park with an area of 15,000.

About us
Shenzhen Weijiamei Silicone and Plastic Electronic Co., Ltd. is located in No.7 Xingrong Rd, Baolong Street, Longgang District, Shenzhen, Guangdong Province, China, 518116.
WJM was established in 2002, covers an area of 15,000 square meters and employs more than 200 people. The factory has passed ISO9001 quality certification, ISO14001 factory environment certification, ITAF16949 automotive system certification, OHSAS18001 occupational health certification.
We have strong engineering research and development capabilities and product production capabilities such as precision injection molding workshops, silicone product workshops, precision mold workshops, auto parts production workshops, and modern boutique packaging production lines.
Our main business is divided into three main segments:
1. Silicone protective cover
For example, POS machine silicone protective cover, game machine protective cover, medical equipment silicone products, tablet protective cover, and other customized silicone products.
2. Plastic protective cover
For example, automotive silicone parts, various customized plastic shells, plastic protective covers, etc.
3. Silicone and plastic combination cases
We accept all kinds of customized silicone plastic products, the main cooperation customers are pos machine manufacturers: PAX, Nexgo, Newpos, and some famous car manufacturers.
